Package: episcope
Title: Episcope: An Integrative Epigenomic Analysis Framework
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yaoxiang", "Li", , "yaoxiang@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Chunling", "Yi", , "chunling@example.com", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Robust and reproducible framework for epigenetic data
    analysis. It integrates functionalities for ChromHMM analysis, DNA
    methylation assessment, differentiation state profiling, nutrient
    stress analysis, and functional mapping to facilitate comprehensive
    epigenomic studies.
